meetups.title: A first meetup
meetups.description: This is a first in-person meetup which you definitely should not miss. We're aiming to build an enthusiastic and engaged community and hope to learn lots about how people are using their tools. Also, there will be free pizza and drinks and it will be a lot of fun!

meetups.title: A second meetup
meetups.description: After the great success of our first meetup, we're back. Expect the same enjoyable mix of networking, pizza, drinks and interesting talks.
